title: Morning Joe 1/27/21
description: Senate Republicans voted Tuesday for a measure that would have declared the impeachment proceedings against former President Trump unconstitutional because he is no longer in office. Joe Scarborough weighs in on where most in the GOP stand.
author: news.podcasts@nbcuni.com (NBC News)
